  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sada hajde da napravimo korak ka ivici <code>Most popular</code>. Potrebno je postaviti ga u gornji desni ugao kartice, pa možete koristiti neke Tailwind utility klase za to.</p>\n<p>Evo kako koristiš placeholder za CSS u Tailwind:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;div class=\"relative\">\n  &#x3C;div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 bg-blue-200 p-2\">\n    This element is positioned at the top-left corner\n  &#x3C;/div>\n&#x3C;/div>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Postavi klasu za <code>relative</code> za paket od <code>div</code> i <code>absolute</code> za <code>div</code> sa tekstom <code>Most popular</code>.</p>\n</section>",
